title: We want the notifications be delivered in time
message:
We want the notifications be delivered in time

From developer docs:
Beginning with API 19 (KITKAT) alarm delivery is inexact: the OS will shift
alarms in order to minimize wakeups and battery use. There are new APIs to
support applications which need strict delivery guarantees;
see setWindow(int, long, long, PendingIntent) and
setExact(int, long, PendingIntent).
Applications whose targetSdkVersion is earlier than API 19 will continue to see
the previous behavior in which all alarms are delivered exactly when requested.
